title: Jennifer Metcalfe 'pregnant with first child' with Geordie Shore's Greg Lake
text:
STUNNER: Jennifer Metcalfe is reported to be pregnant with her first child 
Jennifer and her boyfriend Greg Lake are said to be expecting a baby. 
The Hollyoaks beauty and the Geordie Shore hunk have been together since 2013. 
Jennifer plays Mercedes McQueen in the Channel 4 soap, with her character recently suffering a stillbirth. 
getty LOVED UP: Jennifer is in a relationship with Greg Lake from Geordie Shore Hollyoaks babe Jennifer Metcalfe Jennifer Metcalfe shows off her incredible figure on recent girls holiday 1 / 109 “Jen and Greg are delighted” Source 
The report has claimed that the news has come as a "breath of fresh air" following the difficult plot. 
"Jen and Greg are delighted. They have told their friends and family, who are chuffed too," a source told The Sun. 
"Obviously after her ­difficult time filming her last pregnancy scenes on Hollyoaks this is a breath of fresh air for Jen.
